sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant Consumer as Consumer Repo (CI)
    participant Central as Central Repo (Reusable)

    Dev->>Consumer: Push Code / Create PR
    Consumer->>Consumer: Trigger .github/workflows/ci.yml
    Consumer->>Central: Call Reusable Workflow (uses: central/.../compile-java.yml)
    Central-->>Consumer: Execute Build & Test Logic
    Consumer->>Dev: Report Status (Pass/Fail)
